OL,3,CJarell Quansah banned for two matches
OL,4,Cfollowing red card, Fifa rules
OL,6,FJarell Quansah's suspension is a blow
OL,7,Ffor the Three Lions, as ITV News
OL,8,FSports Editor Steve Scott reports
OL,10,FEngland defender Jarell Quansah has
OL,11,Fbeen banned for two matches following
OL,12,Fhis red card in their World Cup last-
OL,13,F16 victory over Mexico, Fifa has
OL,14,Fannounced.
OL,16,FQuansah was sent off following a VAR
OL,17,Freview of a high tackle on Jesus
OL,18,FGallardo during the England v Mexico
OL,19,FWorld Cup match on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
