OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1783646288
OL,3,CJarell Quansah banned for two matches
OL,4,Cfollowing red card, Fifa rules
OL,6,FThe Bayer Leverkusen defender was
OL,7,Fgiven a straight red following a VAR
OL,8,Freview of a challenge on Jesus
OL,9,FGallardo in the second half at the
OL,10,FEstadio Azteca, but Thomas Tuchel's
OL,11,Fmen hung on for a famous 3-2 victory.
OL,13,FThe Football Association said it was
OL,14,Fexploring its options surrounding a
OL,15,Fpossible appeal.
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
