OL,3,CJarell Quansah banned for two matches
OL,4,Cfollowing red card, Fifa rules
OL,6,FStill, FIFA announced on Thursday that
OL,7,FQuansah will serve an immediate
OL,8,Fsuspension, ruling him out of
OL,9,FSaturday's quarter-final with Norway
OL,10,Fin Miami and a possible semi-final.
OL,12,FA FIFA statement read: "The FIFA
OL,13,FDisciplinary Committee has imposed the
OL,14,Ffollowing sanction on England's
OL,15,Fnational-team player Jarell Quansah,
OL,16,Fwho was sent off as a result of a
OL,17,Fdirect red card during the FIFA World
OL,18,FCup 2026 match between Mexico and
OL,19,FEngland played on July 5, 2026 at
OL,20,FMexico City Stadium:
OL,26,@tD@XOU
