OL,3,CJarell Quansah banned for two matches
OL,4,Cfollowing red card, Fifa rules
OL,6,F"Two-match suspension for a breach of
OL,7,Farticle 14 of the FIFA Disciplinary
OL,8,FCode.
OL,10,F"The suspension will be served in the
OL,11,Fupcoming match(es) of the
OL,12,Frepresentative team of England in the
OL,13,FFIFA World Cup 2026 and in accordance
OL,14,Fwith art. 69 of the FIFA Disciplinary
OL,15,FCode."
OL,17,FAnalysis from ITV News Sports Editor
OL,18,FSteve Scott
OL,26,@uD@TOjwD@FO]
