OL,3,CJarell Quansah banned for two matches
OL,4,Cfollowing red card, Fifa rules
OL,6,FThat was then lifted after Donald
OL,7,FTrump called FIFA President Gianni
OL,8,FInfantino, complaining the punishment
OL,9,Fwas too severe.
